Description: Implements for 'ggplot2' the stylistic elements (fonts, hatched patterns, color palettes) used by 'Emile
  Cheysson' in the 'Albums de Statistique Graphique', sometimes called the pinnacle of the
  Golden Age of Statistical Graphics.
